summary: Bubbly and klutzy, Bubbles is a freshmen attending at The Wacky University (WackyU) majoring in acting. He dreams of becoming a...
caption:
Bubbly and klutzy, Bubbles is a freshmen attending at The Wacky University (WackyU) majoring in acting. He dreams of becoming a cartoon star like his great great grandma Dood. One problem though, he struggles being a toon.

Here’s Bubbles and his old-self, Aqua, from 8 years ago. Man, he went through so many changes since high school. Bubbles is from my other project, A Doods Life. A slice-of-life story of two brothers living out their daily lives in a style mix city, Q’artwn.

Click here to read some facts about him. (Oh, and you can also do this meme if you want.)

summary: The leader of Elton Drifters, he's the protector of Eltown and swore to keep his hometown safe from troublemakers to...
caption:
The leader of Elton Drifters, he’s the protector of Eltown and swore to keep his hometown safe from troublemakers to delinquents. Despite his intimidating demeanor, he’s quite friendly and compassionate of other people.

Man, I haven’t talked about my characters for ages. Maybe a year or two. I need to do that again once I finalize the whole cast and story. This guy, Solo, he’s one of the main characters from my project, The Good Ol’ Days. A comedy romance series about friendship and love between unlikely friends in a forgotten town.

summary: Since I won’t be using this for my school project anymore I’m sure it’s fine for me to upload them. Some characters from a...
caption:
Since I won’t be using this for my school project anymore I’m sure it’s fine for me to upload them.

Some characters from a planned animation that I won’t be going through with anymore due to time limit. Doesn’t mean I’m gonna give up on the story though, maybe just turn it into a personal project like a comic.

Em is the barista for a cafe who has to deal with a rude patron to the point that her monstrous form slips out in order to deal with the problem.
Brendan is said annoying patron, his rude and egotistic behaviour disturbs those around him in the unknown cafe.
